<lb n="0286a16"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>菩薩訶色欲法<note n="0286004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0286004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔經〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0286004"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0286a17"/>
<lb n="0286a18"/><byline type="Translator">後秦三藏鳩摩羅什譯</byline>
<lb n="0286a19"/><div1 type="jing"><p>女色者。世間之枷鎖。凡夫戀著不能自拔。女
<lb n="0286a20"/>色者。世間之重患。凡夫<note n="0286005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">困＝因【三】</note><note n="0286005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">困＝因【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0286005"><lem>困</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">因</rdg></app>之至死不免。女
<lb n="0286a21"/>色者。世間之衰禍。凡夫遭之無厄不<note n="0286006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至＝生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286006"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>。行
<lb n="0286a22"/>者既得捨之。若復顧念。是為從獄得出。還復
<lb n="0286a23"/>思入。從狂得正。而復樂之。從病得<note n="0286007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝瘥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286007"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">瘥</rdg></app>。復思
<lb n="0286a24"/>得病。智者<note n="0286008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怒＝愍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怒＝愍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286008"><lem>怒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">愍</rdg></app>之知其狂而顛蹶。死無日矣。
<lb n="0286a25"/>凡夫重色。甘為之僕。終身馳驟。為之辛苦。雖
<lb n="0286a26"/>復鈇<note n="0286009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">質＝鑕【宋】【明】</note><app n="0286009"><lem>質</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">鑕</rdg></app>寸斬。鋒鏑交至。甘心受之不以為
<lb n="0286a27"/>患。狂人樂狂不是過也。行者若能棄之不顧。
<lb n="0286a28"/>是則破枷脫鎖。惡狂厭病。離於衰禍。既安且
<lb n="0286a29"/>吉。得出牢獄。永無患難。女人之相。其言如
<pb ed="T" id="T15.0615.0286b" n="0286b"/>
<lb n="0286b01"/>蜜。而其心如毒。譬如停淵澄鏡。而蛟龍居之。
<lb n="0286b02"/>金山寶窟。而師子處之。當知此害不可<note n="0286010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">近＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">近＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286010"><lem>近</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">近也</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0286b03"/>室家不和。婦人之由。毀宗敗族。婦人之罪。實
<lb n="0286b04"/>是陰賊滅人慧明。亦是獵圍&CB00458;得出者。譬如
<lb n="0286b05"/>高羅。群鳥落之。不能奮飛。又如密網。眾魚投
<lb n="0286b06"/>之。刳腸<note n="0286011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01131;＝&CB01469;【明】</note><note n="0286011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><corr sic="＆CB01131；" resp="CBETA.Maha">俎</corr>＝&CB01469;【明】</note><app n="0286011"><lem>俎</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB01469;</rdg></app>肌。亦如<note n="0286012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暗＝闇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暗＝闇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286012"><lem>暗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">闇</rdg></app>坑。無目投之。如蛾赴
<lb n="0286b07"/>火。是以智者知而遠之。不受其害。惡而穢之。
<lb n="0286b08"/>不為此物之所惑也</p>
